2007-09-29  Stefan Monnier  <monnier@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* term.c (term_clear_mouse_face, term_mouse_highlight)
	(tty_write_glyphs_with_face): Only define is HAVE_GPM.

	* print.c (safe_debug_print): Use XHASH.

