	Lisp elements such as tags.
	(XHASH): New macro.
	(EQ): Use it.
	(SREF, SSET, STRING_COPYIN): Use SDATA.
	(VOID_TO_LISP, CVOID_TO_LISP, LISP_TO_VOID, LISP_TO_CVOID): Remove.

